data.description: Beautiful home in a serene tucked away NE Mesa neighborhood -- Private oasis with mountain views, sunsets, sunrises, & NO NEIGHBORS behind you! N/S exposure, cul-de-sac lot, pool, spa, artificial turf, low maintenance front & backyard...built-in grill & outdoor kitchen area...4 good sized bdrms PLUS a very large bonus room that could serve as another bdrm, office, guest quarters...or whatever you want to use it for! It may work well for a separate guest quarter conversion if desired since one of the walls connects to the garage wall. Master bath has a large custom walk-in shower. Gas stove, granite counters, & lots of cabinets and counter space! Popular open floor plan with kitchen open to family room. Formal dining room, eat-in-kitchen & breakfast bar.
